克莱罗分享舒适的新单曲“Sexy to Some”并宣布新专辑“Charm” https://www.nme.com/news/music/clairo-shares-cosy-new-single-sexy-to-someone-and-announces-new-album-charm-3759026?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=clairo-向某人分享舒适的新单曲性感并宣布新专辑魅力Anagricel DuranThu, 23 May 2024 19:02:22 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3759026 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克莱罗。图片来源：卢卡斯·克莱顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该专辑将继她 2021 年的 LP“Sling”之后</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/clairo-shares-cosy-new-single-sexy-to-someone-and-announces-new-album-charm-3759026">Claire 分享了舒适的新单曲“Sexy to Some”，并宣布新专辑“Charm”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="克莱罗。图片来源：卢卡斯·克莱顿" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo.-Credit-Lucas-Creighton-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Clairo">克莱罗</a>分享了她温馨的新单曲“Sexy to Some”，并宣布了她即将发行的专辑“Charm”的详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/clairo-cover-interview-2021-sling-2995095">克莱罗：“我太害怕了，不敢想象家庭生活会是我所渴望的”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位创作型歌手在她的官方 Instagram 上分享了她的第三张专辑《Charm》将于 7 月 12 日发行的消息。您可以<a href="https://clairo.lnk.to/charm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存 LP</a> 。</p><p>她还发行了主打单曲《Sexy to Some》，作为专辑的第一首试听曲，这是一首舒适的歌曲，歌词是：“<em>对某人来说性感，这会帮助我/哦，我需要一个理由离开家/而且它是只是一件我离不开的小事</em>”描述想要被某人需要。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Claire-对某人来说很性感" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/w18NGVqm0bg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Charm》由克莱罗·米歇尔斯 (Clairo Michels) 和莱昂·米歇尔斯 (Leon Michels)（《Dap-Kings and El Michels Affair》）联合制作。据一份新闻稿称，这张专辑被描述为“一系列温暖的、受 70 年代启发的节奏，在爵士乐、迷幻民谣和<br />灵魂”。</p><p>这张专辑是在纽约伍德斯托克郊外的 Allaire Studios 和皇后区的 Diamond Mine Recording 录制的。它是现场录制的，并采用了从喇叭到老式合成器的各种乐器。 </p><figure id="attachment_3759045" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3759045" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3759045" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo-Charm-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="克莱罗“Charm”专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo-Charm-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo-Charm-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo-Charm-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo-Charm-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo-Charm-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo-Charm-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Clairo-Charm-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3759045" class="wp-caption-text">克莱罗“Charm”专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><strong>Claire 的“Charm”曲目列表是：</strong></p><p> <strong>1.“游牧者”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“对某人来说性感”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“第二天性”</strong><br /> <strong>4.《慢舞》</strong><br /> <strong>5.“谢谢”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“水龟”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“朱娜”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“加起来我的爱”</strong><br /> <strong>9.《回声》</strong><br /> <strong>10.《雪之荣耀》</strong><br /> <strong>11.“4号号码头”</strong></p><p> Cliroo 的最后一张唱片是 2021 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/clairo-sling-album-review-2992272">Sling</a> 》。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/clairo-sling-album-review-2992272">对该专辑的五星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享道：“无论是在音乐上还是在歌词上，克莱罗都在做她最擅长的事情——制作华丽的珠宝，帮助你一步一步地理解自己的世界。 《Sling》的灵感可能来自于过去的经典歌曲作者，但几十年后，我们未来的艺术家将怀着同样的崇敬之情对待科特里尔。”</p><p>在其他地方，克莱罗此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/clairo-releases-new-track-lavender-to-raise-aid-funds-for-gaza-3518989">通过 Bandcamp 分享了一张名为“Lavender”的演示录音，其销售收入全部捐献给无国界医生组织</a>。</p><p>今年早些时候，这位歌手在新泽西州的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-stormzy-clairo-and-more-perform-at-palestine-and-sudan-benefit-gig-3566213">“Artist For Aid”音乐会上表演，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stormzy-and-clairo-lead-artists-for-aid-concert-for-gaza-and-sudan-line-up-3561172">帮助为加沙和苏丹持续的人道主义危机筹集资金</a>。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/clairo-shares-cosy-new-single-sexy-to-someone-and-announces-new-album-charm-3759026">Claire 分享了舒适的新单曲“Sexy to Some”，并宣布新专辑“Charm”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
