rs-RAYE-Yussef.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ivors-Winners-RAYE-Yussef-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ivors-Winners-RAYE-Yussef-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ivors-Winners-RAYE-Yussef-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ivors-Winners-RAYE-Yussef-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ivors-Winners-RAYE-Yussef-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">RAYE</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yussef-dayes">Yussef Dayes</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skepta">Skepta</a>等人均荣获 2024 年 Ivor Novello 奖 - 请查看下面的完整列表。</p><p>在今天（5 月 23 日）的今年颁奖典礼上，RAYE 凭借评委们所描述的“一代人的声音”而被授予年度歌曲作者奖。 RAYE 曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-calls-out-evil-music-industry-practises-claims-songwriters-are-being-manipulated-3618329#:~:text=RAYE%20calls%20out%20%E2%80%9Cevil%E2%80%9D%20music,claims%20%E2%80%9Csongwriters%20are%20being%20manipulated%E2%80%9D&amp;text=RAYE.,%E2%80%9Csongwriters%20are%20being%20manipulated%E2%80%9D.">多次为词曲作者权利发声</a>，在她期待已久的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/raye-my-21st-century-blues-review-3391162">My 21st Century Blues</a> 》发行一年后就获得了该奖项。</p><p>与此同时，尤瑟夫·达耶斯 (Yussef Dayes) 凭借其唱片《黑人古典音乐》(Black Classical Music) 赢得了最佳专辑奖，而最佳当代歌曲则由扬声器角四重奏 (Kwake Bass、Peter Bennie、Biscuit 和 Raven Bush) 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kae-tempest">Kae Tempest</a>的《Geronimo Blues》获得。 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/victoria-canal">维多利亚·运河 (Victoria Canal)</a>还凭借她的歌曲《黑天鹅》(Black Swan) 与约翰尼·拉蒂默 (Johnny Lattimer) 和艾格·怀特 (Eg White) 一起获得了最佳音乐和抒情歌曲奖。与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave">Dave</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a> 、Jo Caleb 和 Jonny Leslie 获得了最佳表演作品奖。</p><p>其他获奖者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">拉娜·德雷（Lana Del Rey</a> ）（国际特别奖）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kt-tunstall">KT Tunstall</a> （杰出歌曲集奖）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀（Bruce Springsteen</a> ），他成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-announced-as-first-international-songwriter-to-become-a-fellow-of-the-ivors-academy-3609695">艾弗斯学院的第一位国际院士</a>。请参阅下面的完整获奖者名单： </p><figure id="attachment_3417930" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3417930" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3417930" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Raye-Roundhouse-Getty.jpg" alt="雷伊在伦敦圆屋酒店" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Raye-Roundhouse-Getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Raye-Roundhouse-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Raye-Roundhouse-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Raye-Roundhouse-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Raye-Roundhouse-Getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Raye-Roundhouse-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3417930" class="wp-caption-text"> Raye 在伦敦圆屋（图片来源：Chiaki Nozu/WireImage）</figcaption></figure><p><strong>最佳专辑</strong><br />“黑人古典音乐”<br />由尤瑟夫·达耶斯、罗科·帕拉迪诺和查理·史黛西撰写<br />尤瑟夫·达耶斯饰演<br />由 YD Music-Kobalt Music Publishing 和 Sentric Music 在英国出版的音乐</p><p><strong>最佳当代歌曲</strong><br />《杰罗尼莫布鲁斯》<br />编剧：Kwake Bass、Peter Bennie、Biscuit、Raven Bush 和 Kae Tempest<br />由扬声器角四重奏壮举表演。凯·暴风雨<br />由 Warp Publishing 和 Domino Publishing Company 在英国出版的音乐</p><p><strong>最佳音乐和歌词歌曲</strong><br />&#39;黑天鹅&#39;<br />由维多利亚·卡纳尔、乔尼·拉蒂默和艾格·怀特撰写<br />维多利亚运河演出<br />在英国由 Second Songs-Sony Music Publishing、Warner Chappell Music Ltd 和 Universal Music Publishing 出版的音乐</p><p><strong>PRS 音乐表演最多作品</strong><br />“短跑运动员”<br />由 Central Cee、Dave、Jo Caleb 和 Jonny 